Sentencas: The oxygen ion conductivity, attributed to an oxygen vacancy mechanism, of yttria-stabilized zirconia membranes used in solid oxide fuel cells is restricted due to trapping limitations.
Titulo: Lattice distortions and oxygen vacancies produced in Au+-irradiated nanocrystalline cubic zirconia

Sentencas: In this work, a high concentration of oxygen vacancies has been deliberately introduced into nanocrystalline stabilizer-free zirconia through ion-irradiation.
Titulo: Lattice distortions and oxygen vacancies produced in Au+-irradiated nanocrystalline cubic zirconia

Sentencas: Oxygen vacancies with different charge states can be produced by varying irradiation temperatures.
Titulo: Lattice distortions and oxygen vacancies produced in Au+-irradiated nanocrystalline cubic zirconia

Sentencas: Due to the reduced trapping sites and high oxygen vacancy concentration, this work suggests that the efficiency of solid oxide fuel cells can be improved.
Titulo: Lattice distortions and oxygen vacancies produced in Au+-irradiated nanocrystalline cubic zirconia

Titulo: Lattice distortions and oxygen vacancies produced in Au+-irradiated nanocrystalline cubic zirconia
